data.body:
VSCode Version: 1.3.1
OS Version: OSX (10.11.5)

I was wondering if it should be possible to define a custom title/label for context menus.
E.g.

``` json
"contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "extension.moveFile",
        "title": "File: Move"
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "explorer/context": [
        {
          "command": "extension.moveFile",
          "title": "Move",
          "group": "edit"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
```
